Hi Tom,
If you do not torque the drums to the axles the O-ring will probably not be 
compressed enough to seal to the axle and the inner dia. of the spacer that 
rides inside the axle seal.  We have had these spacers turn out to worn down 
to seal to new axle seals also!!
